                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I took the prisoner- he said he took the axe because Mr. Lawrence owed him 1s.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was in his employ two years, and there was a difference between us of 1s. - I asked him for it several times, and he would not give it to me; I said I would have something for it, and when I went to his shed I took the pick-axe for the 1s.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18290219-47-person489">
                  EDWARD 
                  LAWRENCE
