                  </persName>
            . When he last worked for me he wanted 1s. more, but I would not pay him more than his work was worth - he came several times, but never asked for it; that was in May. <rs id="t18290219-47-verdict253" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18290219-47-verdict253" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
